 (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/author-f6hExEIODG8dBbnhIj50jQ">Trình Hạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%BAc-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/S%C6%A1-ni%C3%AAn/poem-etE-hEGTs92wsFod18nGvQ">Sơ niên - 初年</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%BAc-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/author-d0pAJju8J6ouE1xCNQH3eg">Trần Thúc Đạt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-D%E1%BB%8Bch/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-nguy%C3%AAn-chi-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-i9gb8qzVj8SPBV0QghIfAw">Thượng nguyên chi dạ - 上元之夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-D%E1%BB%8Bch/author-IIOGalNxPo6P59m-2ijA6A">Thôi Dịch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%AD-vi-hoa/poem-4AmvBPv_0R9PoR8mjcD_Sw">Tử vi hoa - 紫薇花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
